title: Blac Youngsta Interview and More
itunes:title: Blac Youngsta Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had Blac Youngsta stop by where he spoke about being an ordained minister, new music and more. Also after LaKeith Stanfield fixed his mouth to say "The Breakfast Club" was anti black, Charlamagne gave him a very direct but calm "Hee Haw" and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
